{"tid":1023390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱脫歐讓英國一絲不掛 前外相強森之妹電視上真的脫！","createTime":"2019-02-15T17:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T18:32:07.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dca1e9d76155b2877c90647cc49938b660a9d105","tid":1023390,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/d3899181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2Fd3899181.jpg&h=3fcb7d71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲前外相強森之妹蕾秋說到脫歐，就真的脫！(圖／Sky TV截圖)<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n英國保守黨議員、前外相強森(Boris Johnson)是著名脫歐派，強烈主張「硬脫歐」。之前還因為不滿首相梅伊(Theresa May）的「軟脫歐」方案，憤而去外相職位。<br />\n強森有一個妹妹叫蕾秋(Rachel Johnson)，是藉名記者兼專欄作家。她也非常關心脫歐議題，不過跟哥哥不同，她是鐵桿「留歐派」。<br />\n蕾秋周四(14日)晚上了「天空新聞」(Sky News)直播的政論節目《說話算話》(Pledge)，談論有關英國「脫歐」的問題。未料說著說著，她竟然在節目中真的當眾脫了，讓在場的主持人和其他來嘉賓一臉錯愕！儘管電視臺對節目的畫面做了馬賽克處理，然而在場的主持人和嘉賓都一翻兩瞪眼、想不看都不行！<br />\n53歲的蕾秋表示，她的奮力一脫，是為了響應親歐盟活躍分子、劍橋大學經濟學教授貝特曼(Victoria Batemen)的大膽之舉。貝特曼本周稍早前分別在BBC第4電台及《早安英國》(Good Morning Britain)節目中先「脫」奪人，贏得了廣泛注意。<br />\n蕾秋劍及履及、馬上跟進。蕾秋說：「我們遇到了瓶頸，據我所知，如今有關脫歐的評論很難引起別人的關注。」所以，為了吸引人們關注，她誓言，以後每談「脫歐」一次，她就脫一次！蕾秋用「赤裸裸」的方式表達自己的觀點：「脫歐會讓英國變得「一絲不掛」，此舉同時也是為了向貝特曼致敬。<br />\n本周稍早前，貝特曼在《早安英國》節目中半裸出鏡，僅在胸前寫上脫歐害英國赤裸裸」（Brexit Leaves Britain Naked）字句。她指「脫歐」就像是「國王的新衣」，會讓英國的經濟約點完全暴露。全無保障。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3899/d3899180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3899%2Fd3899180.jpg&h=f3617def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲貝特曼在BBC節目中先「脫」奪人，贏得廣泛注意。(圖／BBC截圖)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KjeOL0ajOPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKjeOL0ajOPc&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=0c18792b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KjeOL0ajOPc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190216/1378854.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190216%2F1378854.htm&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=dbd60c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190216/1378854.htm</a>"},{"pid":"593cba552566e803ab2dde3af5a4da2679891d3d","tid":1023390,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9300e3221b15fd616ce7ba2c573c30d018dfe5","tid":1023390,"uid":68944,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"593cba552566e803ab2dde3af5a4da2679891d3d","tid":1023390,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"Ching你都幾重口味⋯⋯"},{"pid":"71123586e2327a74f9edbb92094a6c3f57dd25f6","tid":1023390,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"做得外相都近60"},{"pid":"93eaff34ed2b974e9a358ebf6d81699cda660dd3","tid":1023390,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b9300e3221b15fd616ce7ba2c573c30d018dfe5","tid":1023390,"uid":68944,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"593cba552566e803ab2dde3af5a4da2679891d3d","tid":1023390,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"Ching你都幾重口味⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有巴打瘋狂post 鹹濕阿婆圖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個post有唔少反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f3f0ad7359feb4259aace03e4e94982623c55d","tid":1023390,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71123586e2327a74f9edbb92094a6c3f57dd25